  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_9\\unordinary_ep9_p040.jpg",
    "text": "WHAT DO YOU MEAN [ONLY GOT A FOUR??\n4"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_9\\unordinary_ep9_p041.jpg",
    "text": "But Wam, you should be proud of this score:\nIt proves you're more talented than the average person'\nBULLSH*T! You only gave me a four and you're telling me it's good?"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_9\\unordinary_ep9_p042.jpg",
    "text": "Ah, Miss. You see, using the standard gauging system, a 3 is average, and 5 is considered \"high-tier\" . So you're very strong:\nEven myself ilonly\nYOU'RE A FRAUD'"
  },
  {
